{"id":533621,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":1,"day":20}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"205","ytitle":"","mtitle":"新年画","ftitle":"","authors":["钱永林"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐家汇新华书店　钱永林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞，在这儿聚会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语，在这儿纷飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节日的书店春色浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张张年画映朝晖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年画，画新年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩笔七亿竞描绘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画中人都是工农兵呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看得贫农大伯笑弯了眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望这边:大庆无冬天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油浪滚滚热汗飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那边:大寨花更红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮山棉岭排成队!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快看这:军民雪夜守海疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜墙铁壁不可摧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再看那:插队青年育秧苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光沐浴新一辈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不尽祖国新面貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不够锦绣好山水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年画也是批林的好材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带回队，参加忆苦会!"}]}